Legal & General - Wikipedia






















 






Legal & General

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Legal & General Investment Management Ltd.)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

"L&G" redirects here. For other uses, see L&G (disambiguation).

Legal & General Group plc





Type

Public limited company


Traded as
LSE: LGEN
FTSE 100 Component


Industry
Financial Services
Asset Management


Founded
1836; 181 years ago (1836)


Headquarters
London, United Kingdom



Key people

Sir John Kingman (Chairman)
Nigel Wilson (CEO)


Products
Life, Pensions and Investments


Revenue
£77,969 billion (2016)[1]



